---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import ContactCTA from "../components/ContactCTA.astro";
import Hero from "../components/Hero.astro";
import Icon from "../components/Icon.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About | Jeanine White"
  description="About Jeanine White Lorem Ipsum"
>
  <div class="stack gap-20">
    <main class="wrapper about">
      <Hero
        title="About"
        tagline="Thanks for stopping by. Read below to learn more about myself and my background."
      >
        <img
          class="center"
          width="50%"
          height="50%"
          src="/assets/portfoli_alt.jpg"
          alt="Me pondering"
        />
      </Hero>
      <section>
        <h2 class="section-title" style="text-align: center;">Background</h2>
        <div class="content">
          <p>
            Hi, my name is Ian Mount and I'm a freshly certified at Full-Stack;
            Full-Time Web Development Boot Camp at General Assembly General
            Assembly Logo.
          </p>
          <p>
            "I am a highly motivated and driven individual committed to
            continual self-improvement in every aspect of my work. My objective
            is to contribute to the development of efficient, user-friendly
            solutions that address real-world challenges. While 'Good Job' may
            suffice for some, I consistently aim to deliver excellence, striving
            for nothing less than a 'Great Job' in every task I undertake. I am
            dedicated to becoming an exceptional developer, understanding that
            true empowerment comes from accumulating experience and knowledge
            over time. Therefore, I value constructive feedback over praise, as
            it provides invaluable opportunities for growth and development. I
            eagerly welcome criticism from those with expertise exceeding my
            own. In my search for a professional environment, I seek a workplace
            that not only supports my individual needs but also encourages and
            challenges me to expand my skills and expertise. I am eager to
            contribute positively to a team that fosters continuous learning and
            personal development."
          </p>
          <p>
            To that end I would love to link up with anyone(s) that wants that
            thinking applied to helping solve their problems Take a look around
            and feel free to get in touch if you'd like to learn more about me.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>
      <hr />
      <br />
      <section>
        <h2 class="section-title" style="text-align: center;">Experience</h2>
        <div class="content">
          <p>
            From managing fast-food chains to pursuing web development, my
            journey has honed leadership, problem-solving, and customer-centric
            skills crucial for creating impactful web experiences.
          </p>
          <p>
            Experience as a Shift Lead and Assistant Store Manager cultivated
            adaptability and operational efficiency, while direct customer
            interaction emphasized user-centric design principles.
          </p>
          <p>
            Roles as Assistant Restaurant Manager demanded organizational
            prowess, laying the groundwork for my transition into web
            development through certifications and ongoing learning.
          </p>
          <p>
            With a diverse background, I'm poised to leverage skills in
            leadership, adaptability, and a customer-centric approach to drive
            business success in web development.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>
      <hr />

      <br />

      <section>
        <h2 class="section-title" style="text-align: center;">Education</h2>
        <div class="content">
          <div>
            <ul>
              <li>
                <b>William Howard Taft H.S. / Jeanine Schultz Prep </b>
                <br />
                <p>[High School Diploma]</p>
              </li>
              <li>
                <b>Oakton Community College</b>
                <br />
                <p>190hr [A+ certification]</p>
              </li>
              <br />
              <br />

              <li>
                <b>In House Certifications and Management Training</b>
                <br />
                <i> Attendance of 22% clocked hours per Qt</i>
                <br />
                <br />
                <h6>[topics covered annually [1-8]</h6>

                <br />
                <ol>
                  <li>
                    <b>Human Relations/Organizational Behavior</b>
                    <p>
                      Learn human relationship techniques and leadership skills
                      for building strong employer-employee relations.
                    </p>
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <b> Computer Applications (Technology)</b>
                    <p>
                      Learn the latest software applications for business
                      including word processing, spreadsheet, database, and
                      presentation graphics.
                    </p>
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <b>Business Communication Skills for Managers</b>

                    <p>
                      Develop strategies for effective internal and external
                      business communications, including verbal and nonverbal
                      techniques, writing, and public speaking
                    </p>
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <b> Principles of Management</b>
                    <p>
                      Learn key management concepts and principles to improve
                      business efficiency and productivity.
                    </p>
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <b> Principles of Marketing</b>
                    <p>
                      Learn basic marketing strategies and techniques with
                      regard to the product, pricing, distribution, and
                      communication.
                    </p>
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <b> Human Resources Management</b>
                    <p>
                      Be prepared to handle real employee issues. Learn the
                      skills for human resource planning, staffing, training,
                      compensation, and managing labor relationships.
                    </p>
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <b> Financial Management & Budgeting </b>
                    <p>
                      Learn to use accounting, budgeting, and other financial
                      management tools to create, interpret, and analyze
                      financial information for successful operation of a
                      business.
                    </p>
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    Retail Management
                    <p>
                      Gain broad perspective for all facets of retail operations
                      including: key elements of marketing and promotion,
                      merchandising, pricing, layout, store organization, trace
                      area analysis, site location, and customer service.
                    </p>
                  </li>
                </ol>
              </li>

              <br />
              <br />
              <li>
                <b>freeCodeCamp, CodeAcademy, Udemy, BloomTech, App Academy</b>
                <br />
                <p>
                  [Individual self paced certifications: ("python", "react",
                  "ruby", "HTML", "CSS", "Javascript") ]
                </p>
              </li>
              <li>
                <b>General Assembly</b>
                <p>420hrs Full Stack Web Development Certification</p>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <section class="box skills-wrapper">
      <div class="skills">
        <div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4 icon-container ">
          <Icon
            icon="terminal-window"
            color="var(--accent-regular)"
            size="2rem"
            gradient
          />
          <h2>HTML</h2>
          <p>Proficient in writing semantic and accessible HTML5 markup.</p>
          <Icon
            icon="terminal-window"
            color="var(--accent-regular)"
            size="2rem"
            gradient
          />
        </div>
        <br />
        <div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4 icon-container ">
          <Icon
            icon="pencil-line"
            color="var(--accent-regular)"
            size="2rem"
            gradient
          />
          <h2>CSS</h2>
          <p>
            Experienced in creating responsive and visually appealing designs
            using CSS.
          </p>
          <Icon
            icon="pencil-line"
            color="var(--accent-regular)"
            size="2rem"
            gradient
          />
        </div>
        <br />
        <div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4 icon-container">
          <Icon
            icon="code"
            color="var(--accent-regular)"
            size="2rem"
            gradient
          />
          <h2>JavaScript</h2>
          <p>
            Skilled in developing dynamic and interactive web applications with
            JavaScript.
          </p>
          <Icon
            icon="code"
            color="var(--accent-regular)"
            size="2rem"
            gradient
          />
        </div>
        <br />
        <div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4 icon-container">
          <Icon
            icon="strategy"
            color="var(--accent-regular)"
            size="2rem"
            gradient
          />
          <h2>Django</h2>
          <p>
            Have had experience with building web applications using the Django
            framework.
          </p>
          <Icon
            icon="strategy"
            color="var(--accent-regular)"
            size="2rem"
            gradient
          />
        </div>
        <br />
        <div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4 icon-container">
          <Icon
            icon="paper-plane-tilt"
            color="var(--accent-regular)"
            size="2rem"
            gradient
          />
          <h2>React</h2>
          <p>
            Have had experience with developing user interfaces using the React
            library.
          </p>
          <Icon
            icon="paper-plane-tilt"
            color="var(--accent-regular)"
            size="2rem"
            gradient
          />
        </div>
        <br />
        <div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4 icon-container">
          <Icon
            icon="rocket-launch"
            color="var(--accent-regular)"
            size="2rem"
            gradient
          />
          <h2>Python</h2>
          <p>
            Have had experience with programming with Python for various
            applications.
          </p>
          <Icon
            icon="rocket-launch"
            color="var(--accent-regular)"
            size="2rem"
            gradient
          />
        </div>
        <br />
        <div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4 icon-container">
          <Icon
            icon="arrow-left"
            color="var(--accent-regular)"
            size="2rem"
            gradient
          />
          <div>
            <h2>MongoDB</h2>
            <p>
              Some knowledge in working with MongoDB for database management.
            </p>
          </div>
          <Icon
            icon="arrow-left"
            color="var(--accent-regular)"
            size="2rem"
            gradient
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <ContactCTA />
    </section>

    <style>
      body {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 3.5rem;
      }

      img {
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 1.5rem;
        box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
      }

      section {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 0.5rem;
        color: var(--gray-200);
        text-align: center;
      }
      h2 {
        margin: auto;
      }

      .section-title {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: var(--text-xl);
        color: var(--gray-0);
        margin: 0 auto;
      }

      .content {
        grid-column: 2 / 4;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .content :global(a) {
        text-decoration: 1px solid underline transparent;
        text-underline-offset: 0.25em;
        transition: text-decoration-color var(--theme-transition);
      }

      .content :global(a:hover),
      .content :global(a:focus) {
        text-decoration-color: currentColor;
      }

      @media (min-width: 50em) {
        body {
          display: grid;
          grid-template-columns: 1fr 60% 1fr;
          align-items: center;
          justify-content: center;
        }

        body > :global(:first-child) {
          grid-column-start: 2;
        }

        section {
          display: contents;
          font-size: var(--text-lg);
        }
      }
      .center {
        display: block;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
        
      }
      .icon-container {
  display: flex;
  
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
}
.nav-header {
  text-align: left; /* or any other preferred alignment */
}

    </style>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
